---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Pebble Dashing in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional pebble dashing across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:420px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(3).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 50%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Pebble Dashing</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Pebble Dashing</h1>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;">Full strip and re-dash or targeted patch repairs. One of the most common external wall problems on Middlesex's postwar stock.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The problem</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Failing pebble dash is one of the most common issues in Middlesex's housing stock.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">1960s and 1970s pebble-dashed semis — common throughout Ruislip, Ickenham, Eastcote, and Uxbridge — develop patches where the dash has blown from the render base. Moss and moisture sit in the voids. Left unattended, the underlying render deteriorates.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Sometimes patching is the right answer. Sometimes the whole elevation needs stripping and re-dashing. We'll tell you which the wall needs and why.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#11ADE2;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The Hancock approach</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Match the aggregate. Prepare the substrate. Apply it right.</h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Patch repairs only look right when the replacement aggregate matches the original — size, colour, and application density. We match before we quote. Full re-dash starts with removal of all failed material, substrate preparation, scratch coat, and fresh application.</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Fixed price quoted before we start. Pebble dashing is one of the most competitive-priced services in the set — very low competition nationally.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:64px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(26px,4vw,40px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a pebble dash quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;line-height:1.65;">Patch repair or full re-dash — fixed price, no surprises.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#11ADE2;color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:28px 0 0;">Cancellations less than 48 hours before booking incur a £100 fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
